    "name": "the doll museum",
    "steam_appid": 3316150,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316150/extras/56804fd5e618de9eb2effee86beef903.avif?t=1769764152\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316150/extras_big/56804fd5e618de9eb2effee86beef903.avif?t=1769764152 width=800 height=207 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316150/extras/0a0da79bbdc4902149f7d5e941334e14.avif?t=1769764152\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316150/extras_big/0a0da79bbdc4902149f7d5e941334e14.avif?t=1769764152 width=800 height=259 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Meet Valentine – the cutest chaos queen with enough slay for two!</strong> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316150/extras/18f1b9600b2993e3c6becefaf0e52fe7.webp?t=1769764152\" width=19 height=15 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You’re trapped in a doll museum that hides far more horror than beauty. What looks pastel and cute on the surface is actually a nightmare stitched together from sadness, self-hate and sorrow. To escape, you must survive the museum’s horrors, uncover the truth behind your imprisonment and outplay the Doll Queen’s twisted game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get ready for a game full of cuteness, iconic attitude and psychological horror!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Awaken as a doll in a kawaii nightmare!</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316150/extras/18f1b9600b2993e3c6becefaf0e52fe7.webp?t=1769764152\" width=19 height=15 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Valentine was turned into a collectible by the Doll Queen, a cruel ruler who delights in trapping lost souls and transforming them into dolls to decorate her museum of misery. As Valentine’s bestie <strong>you guide her choices</strong>, helping her navigate eerie pink halls, confront creepy dolls and resist the Queen’s psychological traps. The museum tests Valentine’s confidence, identity and will to fight back.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Dark Secrets Behind the Doll’s Smile</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316150/extras/18f1b9600b2993e3c6becefaf0e52fe7.webp?t=1769764152\" width=19 height=15 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gradually, you’ll uncover Valentine’s dark past and childhood traumas. Each exhibit holds secrets that will enchant you while also frightening you. Some dolls play their own nasty games, while others support you in unexpected ways.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316150/extras/7f011f3ec9381c53623029c8da27accf.poster.avif?t=1769764152\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316150/extras/7f011f3ec9381c53623029c8da27accf.webm?t=1769764152\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316150/extras/7f011f3ec9381c53623029c8da27accf.mp4?t=1769764152\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Explore, run, slay!</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316150/extras/18f1b9600b2993e3c6becefaf0e52fe7.webp?t=1769764152\" width=19 height=15 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You’ll explore beautiful Japanese-inspired rooms full of kawaii details. Interact with dolls, objects, and hidden secrets, and shape Valentine’s fate through dialogues and choices. Avoid dangerous dolls or confront them—the choice is yours. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316150/extras/ad2d557395aa4cb82ce5f3b2070333a3.poster.avif?t=1769764152\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316150/extras/ad2d557395aa4cb82ce5f3b2070333a3.webm?t=1769764152\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316150/extras/ad2d557395aa4cb82ce5f3b2070333a3.mp4?t=1769764152\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Adorable Skins for every Mood!</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316150/extras/18f1b9600b2993e3c6becefaf0e52fe7.webp?t=1769764152\" width=19 height=15 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can customize Valentine’s outfits and accessories and discover all the hidden cats in the museum to unlock rewards!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316150/extras/c93110f0f2e077ba6d5a145f6e2ddbea.avif?t=1769764152\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316150/extras_big/c93110f0f2e077ba6d5a145f6e2ddbea.webp?t=1769764152 width=1560 height=681 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Be the Bestie you want to be!</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316150/extras/18f1b9600b2993e3c6becefaf0e52fe7.webp?t=1769764152\" width=19 height=15 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As her bestie, you decide how to accompany Valentine: a skeleton, a creepy beast, or a cheeky pumpkin head? Your skin is not just style, it’s part of your personality in the museum, adding more fun and chaos to the adventure!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316150/extras/64f612d08d17ac0bb2854ad314c51829.avif?t=1769764152\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Ready to shake up the museum?</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316150/extras/18f1b9600b2993e3c6becefaf0e52fe7.webp?t=1769764152\" width=19 height=15 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you love cuteness, horror and psychological depth, you’ll adore the doll museum. Every doll has their own agenda, every room tells a story, and every moment can surprise you... through scares, humor or emotional depth. Get ready to slay the doll museum in style! <strong>Let’s go, bestie!</strong> 💅</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316150/extras/f41f3f083f7ed358f1408825999bdb72.poster.avif?t=1769764152\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316150/extras/f41f3f083f7ed358f1408825999bdb72.webm?t=1769764152\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316150/extras/f41f3f083f7ed358f1408825999bdb72.mp4?t=1769764152\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interactive story game with cute, unforgettable characters<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316150/extras/18f1b9600b2993e3c6becefaf0e52fe7.webp?t=1769764152\" width=19 height=15 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Blend of psychological horror and cute aesthetics<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316150/extras/18f1b9600b2993e3c6becefaf0e52fe7.webp?t=1769764152\" width=19 height=15 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore mysterious, hand-drawn rooms with Japanese-inspired Kawaii Style!<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316150/extras/18f1b9600b2993e3c6becefaf0e52fe7.webp?t=1769764152\" width=19 height=15 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Escape the dolls or take revenge, it’s up to you!<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316150/extras/18f1b9600b2993e3c6becefaf0e52fe7.webp?t=1769764152\" width=19 height=15 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Funny tarot readings with a sassy fortune teller<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316150/extras/18f1b9600b2993e3c6becefaf0e52fe7.webp?t=1769764152\" width=19 height=15 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique K-pop-inspired songs that make the game unforgettable<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316150/extras/18f1b9600b2993e3c6becefaf0e52fe7.webp?t=1769764152\" width=19 height=15 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover Valentine’s trauma bit by bit<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316150/extras/18f1b9600b2993e3c6becefaf0e52fe7.webp?t=1769764152\" width=19 height=15 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect all hidden cats and fortune cookies in the museum<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316150/extras/18f1b9600b2993e3c6becefaf0e52fe7.webp?t=1769764152\" width=19 height=15 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize Valentine’s outfits and accessories to your taste<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316150/extras/18f1b9600b2993e3c6becefaf0e52fe7.webp?t=1769764152\" width=19 height=15 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dynamic museum: rooms change as you explore<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316150/extras/18f1b9600b2993e3c6becefaf0e52fe7.webp?t=1769764152\" width=19 height=15 /></span></p></li></ul>",
